      <title>巴西财政部长应卢拉要求取消欧洲之行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-03/brazil-s-finance-chief-cancels-trip-to-europe-at-lula-s-request</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于雷亚尔持续下跌且政府考虑的削减开支幅度存在不确定性，巴西财政部长费尔南多·阿达德 (Fernando Haddad) 取消了本周的欧洲之行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-03/brazil-s-finance-chief-cancels-trip-to-europe-at-lula-s-request</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Nov 2024 14:57:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>选举焦虑笼罩新兴市场 投资者纷纷降低风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-03/election-anxiety-grips-emerging-markets-as-investors-slash-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[从墨西哥城到上海，经历了动荡之年的贸易商们正准备迎接新的政治冲击：美国总统大选有可能颠覆全球贸易，并可能扰乱整个发展中国家的经济前景。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-03/election-anxiety-grips-emerging-markets-as-investors-slash-risk</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Nov 2024 14:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>本周美国大选后，美联储及其同行将继续降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-02/fed-and-peers-will-go-ahead-with-rate-cuts-after-this-week-s-us-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[人们普遍预计，美联储和许多富裕国家的同行将在下周再次降低利率，此时正值美国总统大选尚未决出结果之时。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-02/fed-and-peers-will-go-ahead-with-rate-cuts-after-this-week-s-us-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 02 Nov 2024 20:00:58 GMT</pubDate>
